PROCEDURE calc-values :
/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Purpose:     
  Parameters:  <none>
  Notes:       
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/


DEF INPUT PARAMETER ip-est-rowid AS ROWID NO-UNDO.
DEF INPUT PARAMETER ip-eb-rowid AS ROWID NO-UNDO.
